This web based student marking system is helpful to manage student marks easily.

Before you use this software you might read these instruction carefully.

1. This system is running on web. So your login username and password is really important. When you create new password a
always use secure characters. like @ # $ % !. Don`t use easily guessing password like "password",""your_name" etc.

2. This system mainly handle following tasks
    1. Add New Student
    3. Edit Student Details
    4. Add Marks for Student
    5. Add New User
    6. Edit user details
    7. Profile Maintain
    8. Add Schools to system

